    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Up for sale is a driver-oriented 2004 BMW M3 (E46) featuring the legendary S54 3.2L inline-six engine and a tactile 6-speed manual gearbox. This example is mechanically robust, with a recently serviced dual-VANOS system ensuring precise variable valve timing and a linear power delivery up to the 8,000 RPM redline. The chassis has been enhanced with subframe reinforcement, mitigating a common structural weakness of the platform and maintaining the integrity of the M Variable Differential Lock. While the finish shows minor road-going patina, the performance remains sharp thanks to refreshed suspension bushings and a responsive individual throttle body setup. A technically sound machine ready for the apex.",
      "price": 34500.0,
