      "description": "This vehicle is a remarkable example of pride of ownership, offering a perfect blend of performance and daily utility. The exterior finish maintains a high-gloss luster, though a careful walk-around will reveal a few minor stone chips on the hood and a small scuff on the rear bumper consistent with respectful use. Inside, the cabin remains smoke-free and pristine; the upholstery is free of tears or stains, and the dashboard materials have been protected from sun damage. All power features, including the climate control, infotainment system, and heated seats, are fully operational. Mechanically, the car is in excellent health with a documented service history. We recently performed a full synthetic oil change and a multi-point inspection, confirming that the brakes and suspension are in solid working order. The tires have significant tread depth remaining, ensuring you won't need a replacement any time soon. It delivers a smooth, quiet ride with the responsiveness you expect from a well-cared-for machine.",
